        "label": "Brain API key",
        "setup": "Open the Brain Management Console for your tenant and create an API key from the `keys` resource / key-management area. The public OpenAPI spec states the `keys` resource contains the access keys used to authenticate requests and that applications can authenticate with an API key. Public docs no longer describe the exact UI flow; if you do not have access, contact Intellifi support via [support@intellifi.nl](mailto:support@intellifi.nl).",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      },
